ModEntry.Name: Zeta (IH Add-on)
ModEntry.Author: ZipfsLaw
ModEntry.Description:
Zeta is an Infinite Heaven module that is both a modding framework and an in-game mod manager. It can manage weapons, vehicles, custom player models, buddies and more. It's required to use Zeta modules.
